<div class="container px-2 pt-4 sm:px-0 mx-auto md:pl-20">
    <p> Congratulations someone bought your item! The full listing price and shipping has been paid for.</p>
    <br/>
    <h1> If you can the item is no longer available or the details of the item has changed such as the sender address please click cancel listing and the order will be automatically cancelled  <h1>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-5 pt-5">
   
            <div class="sm:col-span-3"  >
            <h1> To procced please select a delivery option<h1>
            
            <%=button_to 'Arrange Shippping', request_courier_path(@order), method: :put, class:"rounded-md  px-10  bg-teal-700 flex items-center text-center text-sm border border-gray-400 font-semibold text-white shadow-sm "%>

        </div>



       <div class=" sm:col-span-2 flex flex-col  space-y-10 ">
        <div class=" flex items-center justify-center flex-row space-x-20">

          <div class=""> <%=image_tag @listing.cover_photo.variant(resize_to_fill: [150, 150]), loading:'eager'%> </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <div> <%= @listing.name%></div >
            <div> <%= @listing.size%></div >
            <div> <%= @listing.price%></div >
          </div>

                    <%=link_to 'View Listing', listing_path(@listing.id), class:"rounded-md  px-10  bg-teal-700 flex items-center text-center text-sm border border-gray-400 font-semibold text-white shadow-sm "%>
                        
         </div>

       
        <div class=" bg-gray-100 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 px-4 py-6 ">

        
            <h2 id="summary-heading" class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Payout summary</h2>

            <dl class="mt-6 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <dt class="text-sm text-gray-600">Subtotal</dt>
                <dd class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900"> NGN <%= @listing.price%></dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
                <dt class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
                <span>Shipping estimate</span>
                <a href="#" class="ml-2 flex-shrink-0 text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-500">
                    <span class="sr-only">Learn more about how shipping is calculated</span>
                    <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zM8.94 6.94a.75.75 0 11-1.061-1.061 3 3 0 112.871 5.026v.345a.75.75 0 01-1.5 0v-.5c0-.72.57-1.172 1.081-1.287A1.5 1.5 0 108.94 6.94zM10 15a1 1 0 100-2 1 1 0 000 2z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
                </dt>
                <dd class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">$5.00</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
                <dt class="flex text-sm text-gray-600">
                <span>Tax estimate</span>
                <a href="#" class="ml-2 flex-shrink-0 text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-500">
                    <span class="sr-only">Learn more about how tax is calculated</span>
                    <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zM8.94 6.94a.75.75 0 11-1.061-1.061 3 3 0 112.871 5.026v.345a.75.75 0 01-1.5 0v-.5c0-.72.57-1.172 1.081-1.287A1.5 1.5 0 108.94 6.94zM10 15a1 1 0 100-2 1 1 0 000 2z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
                </dt>
                <dd class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">$8.32</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
                <dt class="text-base font-medium text-gray-900">Order total</dt>
                <dd class="text-base font-medium text-gray-900">$112.32</dd>
            </div>
            </dl>

            <div>
                <h1> *This will paid out to you when the item has been delivered to the buyer.<h1>
            </div>

            
      
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
